PINWHEELS

1 	package (3 oz.) cream cheese 
⅓	cup grated raw carrots 
2	tbsp. chopped walnuts 
½	tbsp. milk 
	Few grains salt 
	Merita Thin-Sliced Bread

Stir cream cheese until soft; blend with ingredients. Purchase Merita Thin-Sliced Bread the day rolled sandwiches are made. Trim crusts; spread with soft butter or margarine; spread with cream cheese and roll. Wrap in waxed paper or slightly damp tea towel; store ½ hour or longer in refrigerator. Cut in ¼ inch slices. Makes about 40 sandwiches.
